fy.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/capture-one-catalog0064-1667469611599.jpg?v=1667469612" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/capture-one-catalog0064-1667469611599.jpg?v=1667469612 1536w" width="2000" height="1333" alt="德訓鞋耐穿耐磨應用於多情境" title="德訓鞋耐穿耐磨應用於多情境"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-36_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-37_"><p class="sc-tAExr gPiqEd pf-38_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWBNLc eCTOTm pf-40_">首先，Projext 以慢時尚品牌自居，故總是強調產品機能性、耐用性，讓消費者能以一雙鞋就是用於多種情境。德訓鞋全名為「德軍訓練鞋」俗稱 GT (German Trainer)，最早出現在 1970 年代，因其絕佳的避震、耐磨、和舒適性，所以被軍隊當作訓練時專用的鞋款。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-41_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-42_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-eldieg TLJRF pf-43_"></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-44_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-45_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-cTAqQK eHolsa pf-46_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWBNLc eCTOTm pf-48_">延續經典，歷史底蘊深厚的德訓鞋</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-49_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-50_"><div title="歷史底蘊深厚的德訓鞋" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-51_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/capture-one-catalog0030-1667443376353.jpg?v=1667443378" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/capture-one-catalog0030-1667443376353.jpg?v=1667443378 1536w" width="2000" height="1333" alt="歷史底蘊深厚的德訓鞋" title="歷史底蘊深厚的德訓鞋"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-52_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-53_"><p class="sc-tAExr gPiqEd pf-54_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWBNLc eCTOTm pf-56_">第二，Projext 喜歡將經典延續、賦予新生。除了鞋內採用千年日本和紙，德訓鞋也具有非常深厚的歷史底蘊。</span></p><p class="sc-tAExr gPiqEd pf-57_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWBNLc eCTOTm pf-59_">德訓鞋主要為軍隊中使用，在早期民間並不普遍，同時，軍方為防範軍用設備流入至市面，在軍人退伍前，其所穿過的鞋款均須打孔記錄或丟棄；直至柏林圍牆倒塌、德軍人員精簡，德訓鞋才開始正式的湧入民間二手店。<br><br>隨著時間的推移，以及部分鞋廠陸續推出自家的德訓鞋款式，讓這雙具有歷史韻味的的德訓鞋重回大眾眼光，<span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);"><a href="/pages/about" target="_self"><b><u>Projext</u></b></a> </span>也不例外。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-60_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-61_"><div data-pf-type="Block" class="sc-eldieg TLJRF pf-62_"></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-63_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-64_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-cTAqQK eHolsa pf-65_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWBNLc eCTOTm pf-67_">品牌 DNA，飛織技術減少浪費</span></h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-68_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-69_"><div title="GT德訓鞋採用飛織技術減少浪費" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-70_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/gt_description_01-1667443798900.png?v=1667443802" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/gt_description_01-1667443798900.png?v=1667443802 1536w" width="800" height="533" alt="GT德訓鞋採用飛織技術減少浪費" title="GT德訓鞋採用飛織技術減少浪費"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-71_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-72_"><p class="sc-tAExr gPiqEd pf-73_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWBNLc eCTOTm pf-75_">第三，Projext 以永續為品牌 DNA，Projext 的<a href="/products/papier-gt-white" target="_self"><b><u style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);">德訓鞋</u></b></a>採用「飛織技術」以減少浪費，飛織技術是一個跨界的產品，不僅材料規格多樣，鞋面紋理變化也可以很豐富。</span></p><p class="sc-tAExr gPiqEd pf-76_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWBNLc eCTOTm pf-78_">這項技術是由電腦橫機編織出的鞋面，除了減少浪費之外，更是輕便、透氣、且與足面貼合度高、包裹性強，活動起來更為靈活舒適。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-79_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-80_"><div title="projext GT德訓鞋可直接機洗" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-81_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/gt_description_05-1667444031699.png?v=1667444043" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/gt_description_05-1667444031699.png?v=1667444043 1536w" width="2501" height="1667" alt="projext GT德訓鞋可直接機洗" title="projext GT德訓鞋可直接機洗"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-82_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-83_"><p class="sc-tAExr gPiqEd pf-84_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWBNLc eCTOTm pf-86_">同時，受惠於飛織技術，僅需要放入專門的洗鞋帶，就可以整雙放入洗衣機內清洗，儘管強勁的洗力也不擔心鞋體變形受損。<br><br>此外，<a href="/products/papier-gt-black" target="_self"><b style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);"><u>Projext 和紙德訓鞋</u></b></a>全鞋所使用的木源均來自加拿大、和紙來源為日本四國，兩者均有國際林業認證組織「森林管理委員會」（Forest Stewardship Council: FSC）標章，也就是說其所取得之紙漿或相關產品，是以正當管道所製，以保護森林永續。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-87_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-88_"><div data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-89_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/pexelsoliversjostrom931018-1-1667469469626.jpg?v=1667469471" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/pexelsoliversjostrom931018-1-1667469469626.jpg?v=1667469471 1536w" width="1024" height="1057"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-90_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-91_"><p class="sc-tAExr gPiqEd pf-92_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWBNLc eCTOTm pf-94_">Projext 的德訓鞋鞋面背就是使用了吸濕排汗、抗菌防臭的「和紙紗」。<br><br>一般和紙和棉材料，對於排濕的能力懸殊，人體在行走時，一天平均腳底會排出 500ml 的水，若有更好的透氣排濕效果，是對足部保養的重要關鍵。<br><br>在機能性上，Projext 做了許多相應的檢驗報告，以和紙布為內襯的德訓鞋能在一秒內將測試的水全數吸乾，能有效的讓足部處於一個健康的環境。<br><br>此外，和紙也兼具了抗菌功能，日本檢驗局表明，Projext 的德訓鞋獲得了超越標準 (99.8%) 將近 30% 的抗菌力。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO pf-95_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-cLpAjG eSApOI pf-96_"><div title="德訓鞋橡膠大底" data-pf-type="Image" class="sc-jgrJph bzUUvT pf-97_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/gt_description_04-1667445802670.png?v=1667445806" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0560/7607/5157/t/25/assets/gt_description_04-1667445802670.png?v=1667445806 1536w" width="1024" height="683" alt="德訓鞋橡膠大底" title="德訓鞋橡膠大底"/></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-ezbkAF A-dmbO 